    <div class="main review-item" id="6529727">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6529727/" class="title-link">关于大革命前夕法国社会思想状况的全面调查报告</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6529727"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/54926672/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u54926672-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/54926672/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">贪凉</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-01-29"
      class="main-meta">2014-01-29 21:31:21</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6529727_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  达尼埃尔•莫尔内1933年的这本《法国大革命的思想起源》可以说是关于旧制度晚期整个法国社会思想的一份全面的调查报告。笔者认为这部书在某种程度上可以作为工具书使用，其涉及的资料时间长、范围大、类型全。相信不论研究大革命前夕法国社会思想状况的任何选题，都可以从这...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6529727_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6529727_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










